        <div style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; font-size:1.6rem; font-weight:800; color:#e05c5c; line-height:1;">8–12g</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.78rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55); margin-top:4px;">typical breakfast</div>
      </div>
